      <title>纽约市全球广场业主寻求 9.4 亿美元抵押贷款协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/nyc-s-worldwide-plaza-owners-seek-deal-on-940-million-mortgage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位不愿透露姓名的知情人士透露，曼哈顿全球广场的业主，包括 SL Green Realty Corp. 和 RXR，正在就修改办公大楼 9.4 亿美元的优先抵押贷款进行谈判，此前这笔债务已转移到一家特殊服务机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/nyc-s-worldwide-plaza-owners-seek-deal-on-940-million-mortgage</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 14:10:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
